            "content": "<ol><li><strong>Peach Polish Booty Scrub</strong> – A gentle scrub made for your booty and bikini area. Smooths texture and softens rough patches without irritation.</li><li><strong>Bye Bye Acne Booty Mask</strong> – A detoxifying powder mask powered by charcoal and clays to dry out breakouts and clear clogged pores.</li><li><strong>Peach Polish Skin Perfecting Serum</strong> – Powered by glycolic and salicylic acids, this formula helps unclog pores, fade bumps, and treat strawberry skin.</li><li><strong>Skin Smoother Shaving Gel</strong> – A rich, clear gel that cushions your shave for a razor-glide finish. Helps prevent nicks, burns, and bumps.</li><li><strong>Skin Smoother Aftershave Oil</strong> – Lightweight and soothing, this oil calms redness, moisturizes, and prevents the appearance of ingrowns. </li><li><strong>Intimate Wash</strong> – A gentle daily cleanser for the intimate area. Balances pH, removes odor, and supports a healthy microbiome.</li><li><strong> Bikini Perfume</strong> – A soft mist designed for your bikini area.  <strong>Strawberry Candy</strong> scented for all-day freshness.</li></ol>",
